column16: Yunel Escobar flies out to center fielder Leonys Martin.
Ryan Hanigan singles on a line drive to left fielder Michael Choice.   Sean Rodriguez to 2nd.
Brandon Guyer pops out to first baseman Prince Fielder in foul territory.
Sean Rodriguez reaches on a throwing error by third baseman Adrian Beltre.
Logan Forsythe flies out to right fielder Jim Adduci.
Evan Longoria flies out to left fielder Shin-Soo Choo.
Ben Zobrist walks.   Wil Myers to 2nd.
Desmond Jennings grounds into a double play, shortstop Elvis Andrus to second baseman Donnie Murphy to first baseman Prince Fielder.   Yunel Escobar out at 2nd.
Yunel Escobar singles on a soft line drive to center fielder Leonys Martin.
Ryan Hanigan homers (1) on a fly ball to left field.   Sean Rodriguez scores.    Brandon Guyer scores.
Brandon Guyer reaches on a fielding error by third baseman Adrian Beltre.
Sean Rodriguez doubles (1) on a line drive to center fielder Leonys Martin.
Logan Forsythe grounds out, second baseman Donnie Murphy to first baseman Prince Fielder.
